quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,151,"Manyililani yanti, ŵanganyao ni unami ŵao akuŵechetaga yanti:"
  37,152,"“Allah aŵeleche (ŵanache ŵachikongwe ŵali Achimalaika).” Soni chisimu ŵanganyao ŵaunami kusyene."
  37,153,"Ana (Allah) jusagwile ŵanache ŵachikongwe kwaleka ŵachilume?"
  43,40,"Ana mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) mpaka mwapikanasye asiiwa, kapena kwajongolela ŵangalola ni ŵali mkupotela kwakuonechela?"
  43,41,"Sano naga tuntyosye kwene (m’duniya muno nkanitunnosye ilagasyo yao), basi (nkakayichila ya kwalagasya kwao), chisimu Uwwe ŵanganyao tuchauchisya mbusyo (syakupoteka nnope)."
  43,42,"Kapena chitunnosye kwene (ni meso genu nkanim’bwe) ayila (ilagasyo) yatwapele chilanga, basi chisimu Uwwe tukwete ukombosi pa ŵanganyao."
  44,25,"Ana migunda jilingwa jaŵajilesile ni achitutumule!"
  44,26,"Ni mimela ni pamalo pambone!"
  44,27,"Ni chindimba (chekulungwa) chaŵaliji nkulisengwachisya nacho!"
  45,16,"Soni chisimu pamasile patwapele ŵanache ŵa Israila Chitabu, malamusi kwisa soni utume, ni twapele ichindu yambonembone, ni twachimbichisye kupunda iwumbe yosope (yandaŵi jao)."
  45,17,"Ni twapele maumboni gakuonechela pa ichindu (ya dini), ni nganatindana ikaŵeje panyuma pakwaichilila umanyilisi ligongo lya litima lyalyaliji sikati jao, chisimu Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) tachijiilanya chilikati chao lisiku lya Kiyama pa ichindu yaŵaliji nkutindana pa yalakweyo."
  45,18,"Kaneka tum’bisile (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) pachanya petala lya chilamusi (cha dini), basi likuyaani, ni nkakuuya isako ya aŵala ŵangali chachimanyi."
  46,4,"Jilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ): “Ana nkuiona uli ayila yankuiwomba kunneka Allah? Munosyani, ana ni upandechi wetaka waigumbile? Kapena ikwete yalakweyo liunjili lyakamusyangana (najo Allah) ku mawunde? Mumbani chitabu chachapali nkanichiŵe achi (cha Qur’an), kapena sigasiga sya umanyilisyi (syakutendela umboni yagalagatila isanamu), nam’baga jenumanja nkuŵecheta yakuona.”"
  46,5,"Ana ni nduni jwali jwakupotela nnope kumpunda mundu jwaakuiwomba inepe yangaŵaga Allah, ayila yangaŵa nkwajanga mpaka lisiku lya Kiyama, soni yalakwe ngaikumanyilila ya maduwa gao (kuti akuiwomba)."
  46,6,"Soni patachisonganganyisyidwa ŵandu tiyichiŵa (isanamuyo) amagongo ŵao, ni tiyichiŵa ili nkuikana ibada yao (yaŵaaliji nkuigalagatila)."